text: Kamal Singh may refer to: *Kamal Singh (cricketer, born 1955), see List of Guyanese representative cricketers *Kamal Singh (Indian cricketer) (born 2000), Indian cricketer *Kamal Singh Airee (born 2000), Nepalese cricketer *Kamal Singh Dao, aide of Veer Surendra Sai during the Sambalpur uprising against the British *Kamal Singh Malik (born 1966), Indian politician, member of the 17th Legislative Assembly of Uttar Pradesh of India *Kamal Singh Narzary, member of Assam Legislative Assembly from Bijni Assembly constituency in Chirang district
title: Kamal Singh
